General.Name: Questback Group AS
General.Description: Questback Group AS provides SaaS solutions for collecting, analyzing, and acting on customer and employee feedback in Norway, Sweden, Finland, and internationally. The company provides solutions for employee and customer experience, as well as market research. It also offers subscription and support services; and professional services, including consultation services to support the business process mapping, configuration, data migration, integration, and training. The company was formerly known as Questback II AS. Questback Group AS was founded in 2000 and is based in Oslo, Norway.
